snippet.title: Slime Rancher - Slime Science Update! - Unlocking The Shop - Slime Rancher Gameplay Highlights
snippet.description:
Welcome back to another episode of Slime Rancher! So theres been a lot going on in Slime Rancher since the last time we played most importantly the Slime Science Update is here! In Slime Science you use the your slimes plort to build different contraptions that help you in your slime wrangling endevors! In this first episode we focus on money-making and buying the slime science centre. I hope you enjoyed this episode of Slime Rancher, thanks for watching and liking.

Slime Rancher Season 2 Playlist: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEngsjAeWQXgImQKUEt5AWAWVQtKGw0xm

Season 1 Slime Rancher: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLEngsjAeWQXg8RcY4wLd29SkmvgH6XWAt

Slime Rancher is the tale of Beatrix LeBeau, a plucky, young rancher who sets out for a life a thousand light years away from Earth on the ‘Far, Far Range’ where she tries her hand at making a living wrangling slimes.

☆Merch: http://draegast.fanfiber.com/
